{"id": 2697, "genre": 1001, "title": "日常里，你都有哪些观影后遗症？", "description": "你都是怎么被电影细节影响的，大概就是看完深夜食堂后养成了吃宵夜的“胖习”。", "record_count": 2296, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201812270941460vcHZTr2nU7xyRKI.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-01-08T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 322048, "content": "看电影前都要看下豆瓣评分和短评等，结合自身经验在决定看否，若是院线片，还会参考猫眼评分和淘票票评分，完后会去豆瓣评论评分。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 759065}, {"id": 321537, "content": "一看豆瓣，二搜索背景故事或关联人物，比如看完毒液我要去搜屠杀，血清等", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346634}, {"id": 322049, "content": "烂片看多了 现在必看剧透 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1554364}, {"id": 321538, "content": "看完狩猎", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1353851}, {"id": 321539, "content": "看完电影《call me by ur name》后看见蓝色都能想到那个封面", "image": "img/option/option/20190108151955jaeC6InuPrTSchH0.jpg", "praise_count": 76, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1552438}, {"id": 321540, "content": "看过《蝙蝠侠：黑暗骑士》以后开始一直思考关于正义的问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1341302}, {"id": 321541, "content": "不会在同一天在看一部", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434408}, {"id": 322053, "content": "感觉像是在电影中活了一次", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1554341}, {"id": 321542, "content": "了解故事背景，是否是真实事件改变，结果怎么样", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1320043}, {"id": 321544, "content": "看完就去微博看影评", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1552472}, {"id": 321545, "content": "看完《星空》以后决定好好过自己的高中生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1552472}, {"id": 321546, "content": "看完国产电影后就骂自己SB", "image": null, "praise_count": 70, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 596413}, {"id": 324618, "content": "去影院看完电影会留票根收藏，会去搜豆瓣影评，想了解更多会找相关资料，碰到好看的电影会疯狂安利给朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1567272}, {"id": 321547, "content": "很容易将电影中的氛围代入现实。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1267478}, {"id": 321553, "content": "看完《妖猫传》一碰到黑猫就会问你是不是白鹤少年", "image": "img/option/option/20190108163016neDoKiGwCRZU4PYx.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1277667}, {"id": 321554, "content": "看完龙猫对肉肉的人有了一股莫名的好感。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1068559}, {"id": 321555, "content": "一般只有看完恐怖片才有观影后遗症", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1510465}, {"id": 322835, "content": "每看一部电影都要看看影片末尾有没有彩蛋。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1428892}, {"id": 322069, "content": "看完后，会去看看评分和解读，还有评论", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1544583}, {"id": 321558, "content": "带入剧情设定沉迷半天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1177412}, {"id": 322582, "content": "看完电影累到好想在大厅睡一觉再回家", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1310603}, {"id": 324638, "content": "找原声带", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 737671}, {"id": 321571, "content": "有些伤感的电影，看完久久不能释怀，感觉自己是电影里的一位角色，或见证者", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 716803}, {"id": 322595, "content": "看到开头就猜到结局", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1557762}, {"id": 321573, "content": "看了《让子弹飞》，喜欢说英文单词", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1550031}, {"id": 321576, "content": "看到喜欢的电影，把导演的其他作品都看一遍", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252535}, {"id": 321578, "content": "看完日剧《四重奏》，去洗了牙", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252535}, {"id": 321839, "content": "看了《溫故1942》之後吃放特別香，總覺得吃不飽", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1223542}, {"id": 321840, "content": "吃飯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1223542}, {"id": 321585, "content": "看完电影总会百度一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1552543}, {"id": 321587, "content": "去厕所。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1513949}, {"id": 321590, "content": "害怕电影结束，突然心被抽得半空的感觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1441233}, {"id": 321846, "content": "看完《霸王别姬》，就不忍心听“看大王在帐中和衣睡稳”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1553535}, {"id": 321591, "content": "每一部电影都要写观后感长短都有", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1498204}, {"id": 321592, "content": "看了盗梦空间后，走在街上觉得都是监控的人，做梦醒来会想是不是还在一个梦里", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 172446}, {"id": 321593, "content": "听歌的时候看世界就仿佛眼睛是镜头，生活是电影片段", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1469101}, {"id": 321594, "content": "看名家点评", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1523979}, {"id": 321595, "content": "看到恐怖情节以后不敢睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1535496}, {"id": 319036, "content": "看过《熔炉》以后对所有“小学校长”都有莫名的警惕", "image": null, "praise_count": 84, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 321596, "content": "自从看过人肉叉烧包，我女朋友开始不吃肉了，包子都不吃了。这也就算了，主要我也要跟着受罪了😂", "image": "img/option/option/20190108182737ubLg4vhNZXJrMcTw", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1552569}, {"id": 322364, "content": "每次看到请回答1988的剧照都会漏出一脸老母亲的微笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1555580}, {"id": 321597, "content": "看完超级英雄电影以后，刚走出电影院那会儿就觉得自己出门是为了拯救世界", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1552344}, {"id": 319038, "content": "看过《素媛》就再也不敢让孩子单独去上学", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 321598, "content": "看完文艺电影总要像那么回事地思索一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1507192}, {"id": 321599, "content": "总是会认为有魔法存在（没错我看的就是格林德沃之罪……）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1551779}, {"id": 319040, "content": "看《步履不停》对炸玉米饼总是念念不忘", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 321600, "content": "深夜看完电影后总会失眠\n以前想着自己如果是电影中的人物会做出怎样的抉择\n现在为自己如果作为电影幕后人员会怎么去创作而产生间歇性冲动兴奋", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1546697}, {"id": 321601, "content": " 没事，看完电影后就会淘宝上去搜索电影周边。还有一些观看之前的有关电影", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1552582}, {"id": 321602, "content": "看了《驴得水》后的那几天怎么也笑不出来", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1552581}, {"id": 321858, "content": "看了几集《越狱》后，眼神看事情的时候很自然微眯，仿佛自己就是男主。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1553579}]}